{
  "ref": "carl",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Carl",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [],
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What ales are you serving?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "We serve Crombwick's finest Bloody Bracer, that is all."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Sounds rough, how much?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "99 of you finest coins."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Alright, one Bloody Bracer, if that's all you have."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "I said 99 coins! You haven't got 99 coins!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Sorry, I'll come back another day."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Thanks, Carl."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "99 coins? That's ridiculous!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "What can I say? The ingredients are locally sourced so it's high quality, I promise."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Well, I guess I shouldn't shoot the messenger."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "So..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What can you tell me about this town?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "I've not been here long myself, so I'm afraid I may not be of much help."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What happened to the previous barkeep?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Oh, he had to leave."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "How come?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Scared of turning."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Turning?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Yes, into a sleeper."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Oh right! You see, for a second there I thought you were talking about vampyres."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Ha ha! We, err, don't see many of those types around here. No, no, not at all."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "If you say so."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "I do. So..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Actually, I'm no longer thirsty."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Oh, the red thirst will be upon you soon."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Excuse me?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Carl",
              "text": "Just a jest, traveller."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Oh."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}